Tech stack:
- Python 3.11+
- Flask
- requests
- python-dotenv
- simple HTML/CSS/vanilla JS

Rules:
- never expose the Riot API key to frontend code
- use environment variables for secrets
- keep code simple and readable
- separate Riot API logic from Flask routes
- prefer small, minimal edits
- after changes, explain how to run and test the app
